PrecisAppointment of the HONOURABLE ELIZABETH A. HUGHES, to be a Justice of Appeal of the Court of Appeal of Alberta, a Judge ex officio of the Court of Queen's Bench of Alberta, a Judge of the Court of Appeal for the Northwest Territories, and a Judge of the Court of Appeal of Nunavut during her tenure of office as a Justice of Appeal of the Court of Appeal of Alberta.
